Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当夏日的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过干燥的风放出光芒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却从我面前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这蓝天白云下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500, 0)}第五夜 死者的药
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你通过摄影比赛最后一关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你太谦虚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快点拍下一个片子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭就快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能拍得出来 理保又不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天她也没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天已经是一个星期没来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果换个主角可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我到理保家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星期好像都没有回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 最近在女高中生中很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是汉方药的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在中华街有卖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃多了意识就会像飞上天一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用靠这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以让她们有上天国的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤的话好像有点色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是种抽象的表示方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是讲抽象的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为NOS为何要分析它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夜灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分析结果是黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是种一跑就停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通往地狱的云霄飞车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 要进入人类的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对夜灵来讲是很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果吃了这东西的人失去意识而四处走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会发生什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工厂已经封锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不知道产品流出去多少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要得到人类身体的夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里都会有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 理保呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闹情绪 今天也是休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果要我代替她做杂务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧 那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都不来吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是徬徨中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她已经发誓得到了永远
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却要那么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为紫藤的轻率
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让理保变成同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然那个时候很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讲得过分一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫 但是你讲过不碰人类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你现在却…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能负那个责任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 讲得真轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信她 理保是个坚强的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定能够接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种永远都不会结束的夜晚的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上还在一起玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是因为药的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保又没来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天又到理保家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去告诉她有葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她还是不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保是自己一个人住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她也发生了什么意外的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很担心她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱讲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修一 还有美香子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你们以为我要跳下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会那做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个星期都没回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪里都可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为时间我要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一付陪丧的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个和理保同教室的女生跳楼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在这重要的日子你却没来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这班里就只有你没有去参加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羨慕那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以死亡真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 恭喜你的电影得奖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空帮我签名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是很温柔的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小学时负责饲养
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一只兔子死的时候 她就哭了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是换了个人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只不过是汉方药
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了就会觉得镇定一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还听到另一个谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保不回家的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为在一个男子家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪里听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在讲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可以相信这种谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到刚才理保那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤 夜灵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就只是被它附身的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保她现在跟一个男子交往着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想想你已经几天没吃东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想尽可能的不去喝东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在我的身体里有东西在喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要…想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快控制不了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得自己已经快要变得不是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像有吃药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 站在那里发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脸色不太好 有在吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直休息都没来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在却又在放学后出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我去办退学了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:11:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 因为我一直都没来上课
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你放心 我并不后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为那个长发的男子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识紫藤先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了 你和那男子在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会被那个男子骗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都可以来上学的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他把你带坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讲过了 我并不后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想吃药吃到连身体都坏掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思 你不了解紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不要乱讲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你都不来和我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲了你也不会相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我已经得到了永远
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能再活在这世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能活在修一的世界里的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有走出录像带中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你后悔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然白天不能够出去是有点不便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在有通宵便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以改上夜间学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我已经变成你的家族之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常的高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球一直在转
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我却被留在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天还开得很漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天却变成种子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我却一点都没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这就是永远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 天要亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生你一个朋友都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了 因为那是很久以前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是美香子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前就觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的理保并没有那么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是拍的人他放了感情下去拍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所认识的理保不会再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人有时都要有依靠才能支持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管那是多么坏的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我 理保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会带你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到和以前一样我们在一起的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:15:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来吧 理保
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用再去理那种家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香子给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不用再受那男子的控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你重新恢复成以前的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像视频中那样灿烂的你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在拍视频时的你很快乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们再一次重新开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重拍一次 我们的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讲过了我们的世界不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人有时都要有依靠才能支持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管那是多么坏的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然特意回来报复
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是怀恨在心的类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解决了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤 还有一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它又想附身在谁上面去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 她只是失去了意识而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非被夜灵给…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果药起作用被附身是很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在挣扎着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个身体里有夜灵和人类的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二个在那里面争夺着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像现在的我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果就这样让夜灵赢得身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会变成像我一样只有夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能活在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的命运里就只能二选一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好笑吧 我是个吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事一点都没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再拍一次电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要再拍你那个笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你的笑容成为永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你不是人类也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不能和你一起在同一片天空下跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就像是视频一样的永远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换来的是永远不能在太阳下散步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说自己以前所住的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要永远的分别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当夏日的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过透明的风放出光芒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却从我面前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这蓝天之下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是视频一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的散出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有宝贵的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那宝物现在仍在闪闪发光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.87,0:23:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有成为最后的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有遗失在什么地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论多么痛苦悲伤的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是你宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Night Walker 第六夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不想要…什么永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波に漂う　月の光　昏睡の中　月の光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走る　独り　暗い　空を　あなたに逢えるなら
